@startuml US-05
title US-05 Filter Games by Genre

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "GameController" as GC
control "GameService" as GS
database "GameRepository" as GR

User -> UI: Select genre "RPG"
UI -> GC: GET /games?genre=RPG
GC -> GS: listGamesByGenre("RPG")
GS -> GR: findByGenreName("RPG")
GR --> GS: games
GS --> GC: games
GC --> UI: 200 OK + filtered list
UI --> User: Render only RPG games
@enduml
